title: Insects Limited Announces Continuing Education Workshops
text:
Insects Limited Announces Continuing Education Workshops The workshops are for continuing education fumigation credits. September 25, 2015 WESTFIELD, Ind. - Insects Limited announced a series of workshops for continuing education fumigation credits. This full-day program is for anyone wanting to improve their fumigation knowledge. Whether you are just getting started and would like information from experienced fumigators to help you pass your exam, or whether you are seasoned fumigator needing to pick up some credits toward your license, this program is for you.
